ubes,\na feature that can be explained by a non-zero density of states at the Fermi\nlevel for metallic nanotubes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Oct 2012 17:50:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-04"}
