se and discuss one important question: since this AFM\nordering is at q=0 (in the 20 atom cell) where nesting is a moot issue, what is\nthe microscopic driving force for ordering and the accompanying MIT?\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Oct 2012 03:32:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2013 01:18:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-15"}
