 in the initial conditions -- we discuss what it implies for the usual\ncalculation in which all walks contribute to the statistics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Oct 2012 15:14:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2013 20:28:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
